      <div class="desc-img-box">
        <img src="/assets/top_1.jpg" alt="良いことを記録する" class="desc-img">
      </div>
      <p class="desc-string-sub">振り返りを通して良いことに目を向けよう</p>
    </div>
    <p>&#x21E3;</p>
    <div class="desc">
      <p class="desc-string">②世界の良いことを閲覧</p>
      <div class="desc-img-box">
        <img src="/assets/top_2.jpg" alt="スマホを見る" class="desc-img">
      </div>
      <p class="desc-string-sub">日常に潜む良いことに気づこう</p>
    </div>
    <p>&#x21E3;</p>
    <div class="desc">
      <p class="desc-string">③自分の良いことを閲覧</p>
      <div class="desc-img-box">
        <img src="/assets/top_3.png" alt="手帳を読む" class="desc-img">
